QuestData.Title: Wiping Out the Witherbark
QuestData.Description:
The bloodthirsty Witherbark tribe has always refused to join the Horde... and now that the Horde holds Arathi, we will succeed where the Alliance has failed.
Drive the forest trolls from the Highlands.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill $1oa Witherbark tribe trolls in Arathi Highlands.
